snippet.title: "Call of DOOM: Black Warfare" DOOM Mod - ALL WEAPONS Showcase
snippet.description:
"Call of DOOM: Black Warfare" is NOW Available.
https://www.moddb.com/mods/call-of-doom-cod-style-advanced-weapons-mod

Chapter list:
00:00 [slot 1] - 6 Handguns and 1 SAMURAI sword (9mm/.45ACP/.357 Magnum)
02:14 [slot 2] - 10 Sub Machineguns (9mm/.45ACP)
05:06 [slot 3] - 12 Shotguns (12 gauge)
10:08 [slot 4] - 6 PDWs (PDW bullet)
11:53 [slot 5] - 6 Launchers (40mm Grenade/25mm Grenade/66mm Rocket/23mm CSgas/.404 Raufoss/Fuel)
14:42 [slot 6] - 10 NATO Assault Rifles (5.56mm NATO)
18:12 [slot 7] - 8 Eastern Assault Rifles (5.45x39mm/7.62x39mm)
21:22 [slot 8] - 8 Marksman Rifles (7.62mm NATO/.338 Magnum)
24:35 [slot 9] - 3 Explosives
25:20 [slot 0] - Tactical Medikit / UAC Satellite Phone


Music List:

DOOM TNT Evilution - Into the Beast's Belly [Cover By DAR] - Map08, Map27, Map30
https://youtu.be/8ixTSEbOKqA

Doom II - Map01 - Running from Evil [Metal Cover]
https://youtu.be/N_CJijCLYVU

OC ReMix #754: Doom II 'Gothic Sandy' [Into Sandy's City (Map09)] by Mazedude
https://youtu.be/TfpGfB_gURQ

Final Doom - TNT Evilution OST #7 - Let's Kill At Will
https://youtu.be/LhYu7a68XGw

Doom - Kitchen Ace remake by Andrew Hulshult
https://youtu.be/qTJMDkpOqHI

DOOM TNT Evilution - Smells Like Burning Corpse [Cover By DAR] - Map02, Map15
https://youtu.be/65T41zlPaBQ

Doom - On The Hunt remake by Andrew Hulshult
https://youtu.be/pXEZNha1fHA

EGT - Doom II - Between Levels // Groovy Metal Remix // (Map 04)
https://youtu.be/RzjVWSTZMs0

Arrowood's DOOM MUSIC BOX - Flame of Nuclear (Short version for CALL OF DOOM trailer)
https://youtu.be/kKspP7nJt6A
